The paper discusses the use of Spectral Normalization (SN) and Mean Spectral Normalization (MSN) in Deep Neural Networks (DNNs) for automation systems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
